# Start drafting daily notes

## Create a `org-roam daily note`

Use this for concepts, research ideas, memos, or any structured note.

- Command to create a new daily note

```default
C-c n t
```

- This opens or creates a file like: ~/org/roam/daily/2025-07-25.org

### Shortcut	Command	Description

- `C-c n t`	> org-roam-dailies-goto-today:	Open todayâ€™s daily note

